{"id:": "/div[1]", "tag": "div", "attributes": {"type": "article", "{http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace}id": "MG-1678-04_276", "resp": "mercure"}, "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]", "tag": "head", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/text()[1]", "text": "[Plusieurs Sonnets & autres Pieces en Vers à Monseigneur le Dauphin]"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]", "tag": "bibl", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]", "tag": "title", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Mercure galant"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/text()[1]", "text": ", avril 1678 [tome 4], p. 276-283."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Je vous envoye un Sonnet qu’a fait M"}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "r"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sup"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[2]", "text": " du Mats pour ce jeune Prince. Il est Secretaire de Monsieur le Duc de Crussol Premier Pair de France, & a du talent pour la Poësie. Il n’avoit pourtant fait jusque-là que de petits Vers qui n’estoient veus que de ses Amis. On en parla à Monseigneur le Dauphin qui luy ordonna de faire un Sonnet pour luy. Il s’en défendit sur ce que le Sonnet estant l’ouvrage le plus difficile, il n’avoit pas assez d’habitude à faire des Vers pour s’y hazarder ; mais ce Prince n’ayant point voulu recevoir ses excuses, il fut obligé de luy obeïr, & voicy ce qu’il luy donna avec beaucoup d’applaudissement de tous ceux qui l’entendirent."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/text()[1]", "text": "À Monseigneur"}], "attributes": {"rend": "center"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[2]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[2]/text()[1]", "text": "le Dauphin,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "center"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[3]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Sonnet."}], "attributes": {"rend": "center"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Vous l’ordonnez, Grand Prince, il faut vous satisfaire,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Excitons nostre veine & tâchons de rimer,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Un tel commandement a droit de me charmer ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Mais il n’est pas aisé pour un esprit vulgaire."}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Où prendray-je un Sonnet ? comment le puis-je faire ?"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Par mille vains efforts je cherche à m’animer,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Nulle sçavante ardeur ne me vint enflâmer,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Du brillant Dieu des Vers nul rayon ne m’éclaire."}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Charmant & digne Fils du plus puissant des Roys,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Qui prenez vos leçons sur ses fameux Exploits,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Et qui brûlez déja de les mettre en pratique."}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Si ma Muse aujourd’huy pour vous n’ose chanter,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Quand vous exercerez vostre ardeur heroïque,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Seray-je assez hardy pour oser le tenter."}]}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[2]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Cet autre Sonnet a esté adresé au Roy sur ce mesme Prince."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/label[1]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/label[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Au Roy."}], "attributes": {"rend": "center"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/label[2]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/label[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Sonnet."}], "attributes": {"rend": "center"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[1]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Le jeune "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Loüis"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sc"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[2]", "text": " est tout prest."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Parle, Grand Roy, sa marche étonnera l’Espagne,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[3]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Tu le voulois tel qu’il parest,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Avant qu’il commençat sa premiere Campagne."}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[2]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[2]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[2]/l[1]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[2]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Il a du cœur, on le connest,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[2]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[2]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Mais pour apprendre à vaincre, il faut qu’il t’accompagne."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[2]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[2]/l[3]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[2]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Tu gagnas plus jeune qu’il n’est"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[2]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[2]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Bien plus d’une Victoire, il est temps qu’il en gagne."}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[3]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[3]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[3]/l[1]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[3]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Tes soins luy nuisent aujourd’huy,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[3]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[3]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Retire pour un temps ta tendresse de luy."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[3]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[3]/l[3]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[3]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Si tu ne veux pas qu’il commande,"}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[4]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[4]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[4]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Accepte son service au moins en tes projets,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[4]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[4]/l[2]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[4]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Car ne vouloir pas qu’il t’en rende,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[4]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[4]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "C’est luy faire envier le sort de tes Sujets."}]}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[3]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Le Madrigal suivant est de M"}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[3]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[3]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "r"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sup"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[3]/text()[2]", "text": " de Roux."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/label[1]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/label[1]/text()[1]", "text": "À Monseigneur"}], "attributes": {"rend": "center"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/label[2]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/label[2]/text()[1]", "text": "le Dauphin,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "center"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/label[3]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/label[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Sur le Retour du Roy."}], "attributes": {"rend": "center"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/l[1]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Grand Prince, le Ciel débonnaire"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Nous fait voir de retour vostre Invincible Pere."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Des Flamans subjuguez les trop heureux Ramparts"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Nous avoient trop long-temps dérobé ses regards."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": "Apres que le plaisir qu’il prend parmy les armes"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": "Nous a donné pour luy les plus vives alarmes,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/l[7]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/l[7]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/l[7]/text()[1]", "text": "Ce Grand Roy si chery des Dieux"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/l[8]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/l[8]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/l[8]/text()[1]", "text": "Revint à nous victorieux,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/l[9]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/l[9]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/l[9]/text()[1]", "text": "À sa valeur tout doit hommage,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/l[10]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/l[10]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/l[10]/text()[1]", "text": "Rien ne peut plus luy resister."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/l[11]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/l[11]/text()[1]", "text": "Tous les Héros pourront admirer son courage,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/l[12]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/l[12]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/l[12]/text()[1]", "text": "Mais vous seul pourrez l’imiter."}]}]}]}